title: ATTENTION Wisconsin: Today is the last day to register to vote - Virginia registration has been extended through tomorrow
selftext:
#Today is the last day to register online in Wisconsin!

* *You can register in person with your municipal clerk every day they're open until election day and on election day before voting.*

**Register here in minutes:**

* https://vote.gov/


----------------


-------------------

#Registration for Virginia has been extended though tomorrow the 15th.

-------------

---------------



#Nebraska registration ends Friday!
